metadata.description: Andy Z's debut adventure in Andyland takes you on a tour of his world, where the sun talks, dinosaurs wear party hats, and anything is possible! "Welcome To Andyland" is the recipient of the Parents' Choice Foundation Recommended Award and includes International Narrative Song Competition 1st Place Winner "I Went To A Party With Dinosaurs"
